From Edward Ojile, Kaduna The Sole Administrator of Jaba LGA of Kaduna State, Mrs Nita Byack George, has enjoined Muslims to imbibe the teachings of Ramadan and pray fervently for the peace and unity of Nigeria. Mrs George, who made the call in her Sallah message to the people of Jaba, advised residents to avoid reckless driving of motorcycles and vehicles during the celebration. She said, “I pray to God to accept and reward your devotion, and may the lessons of Eid el-Fitr manifest in every strata of our human existence.”